凯特，你喜欢我吗？

178
00:11:46,75 --> 00:11:50,35
-Of course I do. -So how come you blew me off?
当然喜欢 那你为什么拒绝我？

179
00:11:50,59 --> 00:11:53,99
-How come you were with him? -I don't know.
为什么要跟他在一起？ 我不知道

180
00:11:54,66 --> 00:11:56,42
I just do this.
我就是这样

181
00:11:56,96 --> 00:11:59,95
I always have to pick,like, the smartest guy...
我总是要挑那个最聪明的…

182
00:12:00,20 --> 00:12:01,79
...or the most talented guy.
或是最有才华的

183
00:12:03,13 --> 00:12:05,53
Why can't I just pick someone like you?
我为什么不能挑你这种人？

184
00:12:08,77 --> 00:12:09,87
Thanks.
谢了

185
00:12:12,31 --> 00:12:13,80
You know what I mean.
你知道我的意思

186
00:12:15,78 --> 00:12:18,15
I mean,like,the sweetest guy.
我是说最体帖的人

187
00:12:19,68 --> 00:12:21,34
You're just so....
你真的好…

188
00:12:22,69 --> 00:12:23,81
You're so...
你好…

189
00:12:25,16 --> 00:12:26,12
...so....
好…

190
00:12:37,97 --> 00:12:40,63
Here we go. Let's get your feet up there.
来，把你的脚抬上来

191
00:12:48,48 --> 00:12:49,88
Good night.
晚安

192
00:12:51,05 --> 00:12:52,41
Sweet dreams.
祝你好梦

193
00:12:59,22 --> 00:13:02,68
I'm gonna put this can right here in case you have to hurl.
我把桶子放在这里 免得你想捉兔子

194
00:13:11,27 --> 00:13:15,36
Please stay on the line. Your call is very important to us.
请不要挂断 我们很重视您的来电

195
00:13:16,44 --> 00:13:19,77
You've been up for 24 hours. Go to sleep.
你已经24小时没睡了 去睡吧

196
00:13:20,04 --> 00:13:21,20
This isn't healthy.
这样很不健康

197
00:13:21,41 --> 00:13:23,11
No,no,I'm fine.
不，我很好

198
00:13:23,35 --> 00:13:26,75
And you know why? Because of all the riboflavin.
你知道为什么？ 因为我吃了核黄素

199
00:13:32,19 --> 00:13:34,18
Didn't you have that on last night?
这是昨晚那套衣服

200
00:13:35,03 --> 00:13:37,02
I stayed at Kate's but nothing happened.
我在凯特家过夜 但是什么也没做

201
00:13:38,20 --> 00:13:39,72
Hey,where were you?
你怎么没来？

202
00:13:39,96 --> 00:13:43,73
I'm so,so sorry. I am definitely gonna see your play.
我很抱歉 我一定会去看你演戏

203
00:13:43,93 --> 00:13:47,37
I swear,your play is very important to us. Thank you for your patience.
你的戏对我们很重要 谢谢你的等候

204
00:13:47,57 --> 00:13:50,54
Your play is the next play I'm gonna see.
我接下来将去看你的戏

205
00:13:52,41 --> 00:13:53,74
How'd it go with Kate?
你跟凯特怎么样？

206
00:13:53,94 --> 00:13:54,77
It was great!
感觉好棒

207
00:13:54,98 --> 00:13:59,75
I walked her home,and it was amazing how much we connected.
我陪她走回家 我们之间心有灵犀

208
00:13:59,95 --> 00:14:01,38
Then she passed out.
后来她昏过去了

209
00:14:01,65 --> 00:14:03,38
But then she woke up.
但是等她醒来

210
00:14:03,65 --> 00:14:06,02
And we stayed up all night talking.
我们聊了一整晚

211
00:14:06,22 --> 00:14:08,42
And now we're crazy about each other!
我们现在为彼此疯狂

212
00:14:10,09 --> 00:14:11,49
You had "the night"!
你经历了关键性的夜晚

213
00:14:12,60 --> 00:14:15,62
When two people realize their feelings for each other...
当两个人发现他们坠入爱河

214
00:14:15,83 --> 00:14:19,39
...and they talk for hours and learn all about the other person.
他们会聊上很久 弄清楚对方的一切

215
00:14:19,64 --> 00:14:20,66
You think?
是吗？

216
00:14:20,91 --> 00:14:23,81
-Did you learn about her family? -Two brothers. One died!
她有几个家人？ 两个兄弟，一个死了

217
00:14:24,01 --> 00:14:24,91
Yes!
漂亮！

218
00:14:32,18 --> 00:14:34,17
This is from the woman at the bar.
这是吧台那位女士请的

219
00:14:38,96 --> 00:14:41,69
Sorry. She thought you were somebody else.
对不起，她认错人了

220
00:14:45,33 --> 00:14:46,80
-What time is it? -One.
现在几点？ 1点

221
00:14:47,00 --> 00:14:48,46
7:15.
7点15分

222
00:14:49,50 --> 00:14:50,93
Watch doesn't work.
我的表坏了

223
00:14:52,20 --> 00:14:55,47
Tommy's supposed to be here soon. We're going to lunch.
汤米快来了，我们要去吃饭

224
00:14:57,94 --> 00:15:01,81
Look,I wasn't gonna say anything to you,but....
听着，我本来不想说的 但是…

225
00:15:02,01 --> 00:15:05,68
All right,I don't think you should be seeing Tommy anymore.
好吧，我觉得 你不该跟汤米来往

226
00:15:06,78 --> 00:15:08,05
You don't?
是吗？

227
00:15:08,29 --> 00:15:12,62
The guy is mean. I mean,really mean. I think you should stay away from him.
那砘锖芏窳樱非常恶劣 你应该离他远一点

228
00:15:13,82 --> 00:15:17,16
Or maybe I should stay away from all men.
或许我应该离所有男人远一点

229
00:15:17,56 --> 00:15:19,89
It's not just because I'm jealous.
我不只是在嫉妒

230
00:15:21,53 --> 00:15:24,00
I mean,I'm not. I'm not jealous.
我不是在嫉妒

231
00:15:24,64 --> 00:15:29,13
Look,the guy actually screamed at this couple sitting in our seats.
那砘锒宰错位子的夫妇大吼

232
00:15:29,37 --> 00:15:31,74
Yeah,and at the end of the play...
对啊，落幕的时候

233
00:15:32,18 --> 00:15:36,98
...he got up,and he just started, like,banging his hands together.
他还站起来 用力拍打他的双手

234
00:15:39,42 --> 00:15:42,01
You don't want to believe me, that's fine.
好，你们不信就算了

235
00:15:42,22 --> 00:15:43,38
We're kidding.
开玩笑的

236
00:15:46,22 --> 00:15:49,35
No one believe me. I'm Mr. Funny to you. Mr. Funny!
没有人相信我 你们当都我在耍宝

237
00:15:49,66 --> 00:15:52,56
-Sorry,Tommy. -What's in the cup?
对不起 杯子里是什么？

238
00:15:54,20 --> 00:15:56,39
What is in the cup?
杯子里是什么？

239
00:15:56,60 --> 00:15:57,69
Okay,it's coffee.
是咖啡

240
00:15:57,90 --> 00:16:00,20
Iced coffee? Tell me it's iced coffee.
冰咖啡吗？请告诉我是冰咖啡

241
00:16:01,91 --> 00:16:04,40
-It's hot -Hot coffee!
是热… 热咖啡！

242
00:16:05,01 --> 00:16:08,50
You idiot! You gonna spill hot coffee all over me,huh?
你这个白痴！ 你想拿热咖啡泼我？

243
00:16:08,75 --> 00:16:13,24
What are you? Just a big,stupid doofy idiot with a doofy idiot hairdo?
你是发型很鸟的鸟白痴吗？

244
00:16:17,72 --> 00:16:20,12
What's your favorite thing about summertime?
你最喜欢夏天的什么？

245
00:16:20,42 --> 00:16:24,42
Going to the beach when it stays light real late.
去海边玩，天色很晚才变暗

246
00:16:29,37 --> 00:16:31,53
What's your favorite thing about summer?
你最喜欢夏天的什么？

247
00:16:32,54 --> 00:16:35,70
I don't know. Probably the smell of freshly cut grass.
不知道 新除过的草地的味道吧

248
00:16:36,07 --> 00:16:37,73
That's a good one.
这个好

249
00:16:42,58 --> 00:16:46,71
Sorry! Sorry I'm late! My duck and my chick had a fight. It was ugly.
抱歉迟到 我的鸡和鸭吵架，场面很乱

250
00:16:47,25 --> 00:16:49,55
We held the curtain for you. Let's go!
我们在等你，上场吧

251
00:16:54,99 --> 00:16:58,05
Vic! Where have you been,baby?
维克，你上哪去了？

252
00:17:02,33 --> 00:17:03,30
Where's Kate?
凯特呢？

253
00:17:03,50 --> 00:17:04,90
She got a job in L.A.
她在洛杉矶找到工作

254
00:17:07,77 --> 00:17:12,64
I've been waiting up all night for you. Where have you been?
我等了你一整夜 你上哪去了？

255
00:17:13,51 --> 00:17:15,94
Where have you been,Vic?
你上哪去了，维克？

256
00:17:17,95 --> 00:17:21,91
Go to the window. I wanna run down to the truck and show you something.
去窗子旁边 我去车上拿个东西给你看

257
00:17:24,29 --> 00:17:26,62
What do you got down there,Vic?
你要给我看什么？

258
00:17:26,86 --> 00:17:29,42
What do you got under that tarp?
帆布底下藏了什么？

259
00:17:32,46 --> 00:17:33,56
When is she leaving?
她什么时候走？

260
00:17:33,86 --> 00:17:36,53
Tonight. What are you doing?
今晚，你在干什么？

261
00:17:38,10 --> 00:17:39,36
I'm coming up!
我马上上来

262
00:17:42,71 --> 00:17:44,94
Hey,you mind if I use the phone?
可以借用电话吗？

263
00:17:50,28 --> 00:17:52,91
Use ours across the hall because she...
去对面用我们的，因为她…

264
00:17:53,22 --> 00:17:54,55
... has problems.
有点问题

265
00:17:54,79 --> 00:17:55,77
Thanks.
谢谢

266
00:17:59,02 --> 00:17:59,85
Sorry,Tommy.
汤米，对不起

267
00:18:00,12 --> 00:18:02,89
I almost spilled this hot coffee on you.
我差点把热咖啡泼到你身上

268
00:18:03,99 --> 00:18:05,66
Yeah,but you didn't.
但是你没有

269
00:18:05,96 --> 00:18:07,12
No,but...
没错，但是…

270
00:18:07,70 --> 00:18:08,89
...it's hot.
这是热的

271
00:18:12,70 --> 00:18:15,30
Would you stop it? It's getting really old.
别闹了，都老掉牙了

272
00:18:15,51 --> 00:18:17,47
I can't believe no one believes me.
居然没有人相信我

273
00:18:17,84 --> 00:18:19,33
I do. I believe you.
我相信你

274
00:18:19,88 --> 00:18:20,74
You do?
真的？

275
00:18:21,01 --> 00:18:24,34
Yeah. But I also believed her when she said I was next.
对，但是我也相信我是下一个

276
00:18:32,39 --> 00:18:33,98
Hey there,little fella.
嗨，小东西

277
00:18:34,22 --> 00:18:36,52
Mr. Fuzzy Man,how you doing?
毛毛脸，你好吗？

278
00:18:40,90 --> 00:18:41,87
Gross!
恶心死了

279
00:18:42,57 --> 00:18:43,43
Idiot!
白痴！

280
00:18:44,50 --> 00:18:47,44
Stupid,little,fuzzy,yellow creature!
白痴黄毛鸡

281
00:18:47,70 --> 00:18:51,57
"Oh,look at me! I'm so cute! I'm a little chick who's disgusting!"
你看我，我好可爱 我是恶心的小鸡！

282
00:18:51,84 --> 00:18:54,33
You're so stupid! How are you not yet extinct?
笨蛋！你怎么还没绝种？

283
00:18:57,45 --> 00:18:59,18
What are you quacking about?
你叫什么叫？

284
00:18:59,62 --> 00:19:01,24
Dumb Donald Dodo!
白痴唐老鸭

285
00:19:05,36 --> 00:19:07,69
Step away from the duck.
离鸭子远一点

286
00:19:11,13 --> 00:19:13,19
Sorry,little Mr. Chickadee.
很抱歉，小鸡鸡

287
00:19:13,40 --> 00:19:15,39
Sorry you went doody in my hand!
谁叫你在我手上撇条！

288
00:19:18,47 --> 00:19:20,63
I guess we're not going out anymore.
看来我们是没希望了

289
00:19:20,87 --> 00:19:21,90
Man!
妈的！

290
00:19:26,34 --> 00:19:30,14
Joey,I'm so glad I caught you. I couldn't find you before.
乔伊，幸好赶上了 我一直找不到你

291
00:19:30,51 --> 00:19:32,41
What's all this about L.A.?
洛杉矶是怎么回事？

292
00:19:32,75 --> 00:19:34,68
They still want me for General Hospital.
“综合医院”还是要我

293
00:19:34,89 --> 00:19:35,75
But...
但是…

294
00:19:36,32 --> 00:19:37,69
...what about us?
我们呢？

295
00:19:39,06 --> 00:19:41,08
Last night was wonderful.
昨晚感觉很棒

296
00:19:42,16 --> 00:19:44,22
But I can't stay here just for you.
但我不能为了你留下来

297
00:19:45,36 --> 00:19:47,33
So stay for the museums.
那就为了博物馆留下来

298
00:19:48,20 --> 00:19:50,43
-I'm sorry. -Joey,on-stage!
对不起 乔伊上场

299
00:19:51,17 --> 00:19:53,26
At least stay till the end of the play.
至少等到落幕

300
00:19:53,50 --> 00:19:56,34
I'll go to the airport with you. I want to say goodbye.
我陪你去机场，我想跟你道别

301
00:19:56,57 --> 00:19:58,01
Where are you,Vic?
维克，你在哪里？

302
00:19:58,51 --> 00:20:00,77
Flight's in an hour. I gotta go.
一小时后的班机，我得走了

303
00:20:01,01 --> 00:20:02,38
Vic?
维克？

304
00:20:02,68 --> 00:20:03,61
Vic?
维克？

305
00:20:05,12 --> 00:20:06,95
-Vic! -ln a minute!
维克！ 等一下！

306
00:20:09,62 --> 00:20:12,02
So this is it,Victor?
维克，就这样了？

307
00:20:12,92 --> 00:20:15,12
Yeah. I guess it is.
我想是的

308
00:20:22,13 --> 00:20:23,16
Listen...
听我说

309
00:20:25,04 --> 00:20:28,84
... I gotta say goodbye,and I gotta say it quick because this is killing me.
我必须赶快说再见 因为我的心好痛

310
00:20:29,44 --> 00:20:34,04
One thing you gotta know is that I will never forget you.
我要你知道 我永远不会忘记你

311
00:20:34,28 --> 00:20:37,15
But you got things you have to do now.
但是你有你该做的事

312
00:20:37,78 --> 00:20:38,94
And so do l.
而我也是

313
00:20:41,12 --> 00:20:42,14
And so...
所以…

314
00:20:44,62 --> 00:20:47,06
... I'm gonna get on this spaceship...
我要登上太空船

315
00:20:54,46 --> 00:20:58,80
...and I'm gonna go to Blaargon-7 in search of alternative fuels.
前往布拉刚7号星 寻找替代燃料

316
00:20:59,67 --> 00:21:03,00
But when I return 200 years from now...
等我两百年后回来

317
00:21:03,54 --> 00:21:05,74
...you'll be long gone...
你早就死了

318
00:21:06,38 --> 00:21:08,40
... but I won't have aged at all.
而我却一点也不会老

319
00:21:11,98 --> 00:21:15,47
So you tell your great, great granddaughter...
所以请告诉你的曾曾孙女

320
00:21:15,85 --> 00:21:17,08
...to look me up.
叫她找我

321
00:21:19,16 --> 00:21:20,56
Because,Adrianne...
因为爱莉安…

322
00:21:21,36 --> 00:21:22,33
... baby...
亲爱的…

323
00:21:24,66 --> 00:21:26,72
... I'm gonna want to meet her.
我绝对会想认识她

324
00:21:34,54 --> 00:21:36,23
So long,Vic!
别了，维克

325
00:21:44,21 --> 00:21:46,68
It's been two days.
已经两天了

326
00:21:47,38 --> 00:21:48,44
Yeah,I know.
我知道

327
00:21:49,05 --> 00:21:52,04
Good thing it's one of those 801 numbers,right?
幸好是801免付费电话

328
00:21:52,36 --> 00:21:57,29
Phoebe,800 is toll free. 801 is Utah.
800才是免付费电话 801是犹他州码

329
00:21:59,83 --> 00:22:04,46
It has to be 800 because all those big companies have 800 numbers.
一定是800 大公司都有免付费专线

330
00:22:04,70 --> 00:22:05,69
Every....
每个…

331
00:22:06,67 --> 00:22:10,00
Yeah,every big Utah-based company has one.
犹他州大公司都是801开头

332
00:22:11,38 --> 00:22:14,37
Sorry. I'm so sorry. I will pay you back.
真的很抱歉，我会付钱的

333
00:22:14,98 --> 00:22:17,67
And yet she's still not hanging up the phone.
她还是不挂电话

334
00:22:17,88 --> 00:22:19,54
-Hang up! -Hang up the phone!
挂掉啦 挂挂挂！

335
00:22:19,85 --> 00:22:21,25
Fine! Fine!
好啦

336
00:22:28,76 --> 00:22:30,56
Well,I think I broke it.
我好像把它摔坏了

337
00:22:33,16 --> 00:22:36,89
But that's all right. Here's the number where you can call.
没关系，你们可以打这支电话

338
00:00:00,00 --> 00:00:00,00


339
